(42, 18, 30, 19, 63, 4, 5, NULL, 'Satisfaction and Blessing Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of receiving blessings and satisfaction. Both passages emphasize the idea of being fulfilled and blessed in life, with Luke referencing manifold rewards and Psalms expressing satisfaction of the soul.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
