(42, 18, 32, 41, 14, 65, 65, 'spitted on', 'Connection of Mocking and Spitting', 'Both passages emphasize the act of mocking and spitting on Jesus. Luke 18:32 predicts this treatment, while Mark 14:65 describes it occurring during his trial.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
